replies.body:
I was running {{item:3146}} instead of{{item:3116}} as my last item in the build for awhile untill i relized that having the slow = more damage from E and R so quickly evolved to {{item:3116}} 

Cleaver would be good if i was focusing in my ULT more. but it only benifits that. When my ults down i can still kill people and skirmish with my Q and E not to mention {{item:3115}} on hit does go off with my Q just a little bonus :P

So my conclusion is that {{item:3071}} would be the way to go if your going all in on the combo. But i think {{item:3115}} or even{{item:3124}} brings some much needed balance to the AP MF kit.
